<subpara id="RM000000XI9009X_03" type-id="51" category="05" proc-id="RM0250U___00005LN00000">
<name>INSPECTION PROCEDURE</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<atten3>
<ptxt>When replacing the brake actuator assembly, perform zero point calibration (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000XHR009X"/>).</ptxt>
</atten3>
